results.question: After disengaging the PTO shaft, what poses a continued danger and why?

After disengaging the PTO shaft, the machine will continue running because of inertia. Keep a safe distance to the machine until the moving parts have come to a complete stop. Approaching the machine while it is rotating can cause serious or deadly injuries.
